1.将本文件复制到/var/Alumni2012/下面
2.向/etc/apache2/httpd.conf后面写入下面内容：

<VirtualHost *:80>
    ServerName alumni.alumni2012.com
    DocumentRoot /var/Alumni2012/Alumni/
</VirtualHost>
<VirtualHost *:80>
    ServerName info.alumni2012.com
    DocumentRoot /var/Alumni2012/Info/
</VirtualHost>
<VirtualHost *:80>
    ServerName foundation.alumni2012.com
    DocumentRoot /var/Alumni2012/Foundation/
</VirtualHost>

3.向/etc/hosts写入下列内容：

127.0.0.1 alumni.alumni2012.com info.alumni2012.com foundation.alumni2012.com

4.重启apache2
